7, we think the <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/36738/161752/4/109401/?merchant=Home%20Depot" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Home Depot" data-vars-store="Home Depot" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/36738/161752/4/109401/?merchant=Home%20Depot">Tramontina Gourmet 12-Piece Tri-Ply Clad Cookware Set</a> is the best for most home cooks because of its solid construction and affordable price.</p></section><div><section class="d0a27ae8" data-gtm-element="intro"><div class="a7ed89b1 global-cob eefda761 cff8e815 _9f18d780" data-scp="callout"><h4 class="b1dfff67" data-scp="callout_label">Our pick</h4><div id="callout-intro-0-2" class="f4873f0f" data-gtm-element="callout" data-scp="callout_item"><div class="_32e239ce"><div class="_892e4e17"><div class="a35ae31e"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/36738/163977/4/111078?merchant=Wayfair" class="bac232ef product-merchant-link-button" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-store="Wayfair" data-vars-store="Wayfair" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/36738/163977/4/111078?merchant=Wayfair" data-gtm-trigger="callout_product_link_image" data-scp="callout_image"><figure class="_92ef929f global_chapter__arp_image"><img alt="Tramontina Gourmet 12-Piece Tri-Ply Clad Cookware Set" itemProp="image" data-src="https://d1b5h9psu9yexj.cloudfront.net/36738/Tramontina-Gourmet-12-Piece-Tri-Ply-Clad-Cookware-Set_20201001-182156_full.jpeg" width="570" height="380" class="df5db67b _45d01177"/></figure></a></div><div class="d3181b64"><h3 class="_8eb8c80e"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/36738/163977/4/111078?merchant=Wayfair" class="product-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="Tramontina Gourmet 12-Piece Tri-Ply Clad Cookware Set" data-store="Wayfair" data-vars-store="Wayfair" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter