ytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/the-best-small-saucepan/" aria-label="The Best Small Saucepan" data-gtm-trigger="related_content_title">The Best Small Saucepan</a></h3><p class="_17975659">by <!-- -->Anna Perling and Lesley Stockton</p><div id="group-text-8930" class="a189aa06"><p>Among the 14 pans we’ve tested, the <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/32150/153268/4/92714/?merchant=Amazon" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/32150/153268/4/92714/?merchant=Amazon">Tramontina Gourmet Tri-ply Clad 2-Quart Covered Saucepan</a> stands out for its comfortable handle and even heating.</p></div></div></article></li><li class="_0518a4a5"><article class="e1817d6a" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/best-nonstick-pan/" data-title="The Best Nonstick Pan" aria-labelledby="group-title-10570" aria-describedby="group-text-10570" tabindex="0"><div class="_1aa5e7f2"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/best-nonstick-pan/" role="presentation" tabindex="-1" data-gtm-trigger="related_content_image"><figure class="_92ef929f global_chapter__arp_image"><img alt="The Best Nonstick Pan" itemProp="image" role="presentation" src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2020/10/nonstickpan-2048px-8416.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;crop=3:2&amp;width=90" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2020/10/nonstickpan-2048px-8416.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;crop=3:2&amp;width=150" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2020/10/nonstickpan-2048px-8416.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;crop=3:2&amp;width=150 768w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2020/10/nonstickpan-2048px-8416.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=60&amp;crop=3:2&amp;width=150&amp;dpr=1.5 1152w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2020/10/nonstickpan-2048px-